    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>shredded lettuce</strong>, <strong>lettuce leaves</strong>, <strong>chopped cherry tomatoes</strong>, <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>avocado</strong>, <strong>sliced shallot </strong>and <strong>roasted potatoes</strong> to a bowl</p><p>Add <strong>half</strong> the <strong>mustard dressing </strong>(you'll use the rest later!)</p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>dressed salad</strong></p>",
